Package: valetr
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Title: R interface to Bank of Canada's Valet API.
Authors@R: person("José", "de Mello", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="zedemellonetto@gmail.com")
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: jsonlite (>= 0.9)
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Maintainer: José de Mello <zedemellonetto@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides an R interface to Bank of Canada's Valet API (\href{https://www.bankofcanada.ca/valet/docs}{https://www.bankofcanada.ca/valet/docs}). The Valet API allows users to retrive financial data from the Bank of Canada. Please read the Terms and Conditions for the API: \href{https://www.bankofcanada.ca/terms/}{https://www.bankofcanada.ca/terms/}.
